        "TileImage": "$($repository 901f35bc-5235-44b4-ad01-7a3518d60ee2).Image",
        "Description": "A contract has been issued mainly for intel gathering and coverups. Our client, a son of a father who was assasinated, has asked us to free up Yuki Yamazaki&apos;s computer so they can have their team hack her computer. The cause of this is  due to the lack of belief that their father&apos;s death was an accident. Now that Erich Soders has betrayed us this frees up the contract and allows Soders to be exposed. The client has also requested that they kill their inside man incase of interrogation.",
